MBOMBELA &#8211; Lowveld Hospital is trying to help a man with a tumour growing on his chin, but needs the support of the community as well. According to the hospital&#8217;s customer relationship manager, Ms Lisa Volbrecht, Mr Sipho Hadebe (39) is a friendly, hardworking security guard who resides in Barberton. &#8220;He has been struggling with a tumour growing on his chin (ameloblastoma of the mandible).